        "h3": { "en": "Motor B", "zh": "电机 B" },
        "body": { "en": "We refer to the right motor as Motor B.", "zh": "右侧电机记作电机 B。" },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "left:140mm; top:30mm; width:40mm;"
      },
      {
        "h3": { "en": "Mirror", "zh": "镜像" },
        "body": { "en": "This is the right motor — mirror of the left. The cable connector faces right.", "zh": "这是右侧电机——与左侧电机镜像对称。线缆接头朝右。" },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "left:140mm; top:120mm; width:78mm;"
