  {
    "type": "tall-left",
    "page": "25",
    "head": { "title": { "en": "MOTOR", "zh": "电机" }, "small": "motor_30" },
    "variant": "hero",
    "figures": [
      { "src": "motor_30_pulley_exploded_cam1_wcny.svg" },
      { "src": "motor_30_pulley_assembled_cam0_ghfe.svg" }
    ],
    "notes": [
      {
        "h3": { "en": "Two heights, on purpose", "zh": "两种高度，特意为之" },
        "body": { "en": "The A and B belts run on two stacked planes. Set Motor A's pulley (left) to the lower plane and Motor B's (right) to the upper — slide each along the shaft, then lock the set screw.", "zh": "A、B 两条同步带走上下两层平面。电机 A 的同步带轮（左侧）放在下层平面，电机 B 的（右侧）放在上层——各自沿轴滑到位，再拧紧紧定螺钉锁定。" },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "left:40mm; top:20mm; width:80mm;"
      },
      {
        "h3": { "en": "Grub screws", "zh": "紧定螺钉" },
        "body": { "en": "<p style=\"color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 1.5mm;\">The root of all issues.</p><p>Apply threadlocker to every grub screw — no exceptions. Loose grub screws are the most common problem users report; a drop now saves hours of troubleshooting later. Follow the directions on your threadlocker.</p>", "zh": "<p style=\"color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 1.5mm;\">万恶之源。</p><p>每一颗紧定螺钉都要涂螺纹胶，无一例外。紧定螺钉松动是用户反馈最多的故障；现在滴一滴，日后能省下几个小时排查。具体用法按所用螺纹胶的说明操作。</p>" },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "left:140mm; top:110mm; width:80mm;"
      }
    ],
    "bom": {
      "label": { "en": "Bill of materials", "zh": "物料清单" },
